summary: AN ORDINANCE carrying over the unexpended and unencumbered balances in certain 1972 Budget appropriations made from the General, Park, Library, Seattle Center, City Street, Light, Transit, Water, Sewer, Solid Waste, Building Department Operating, General Services Operating, Manpower and Youth Operating, Community Development Operating, Design Commission Operating, Housing and Abatement Revolving, Emergency Employment Operating, Employees' Retirement and Model City Funds to the respective items in the 1973 Budget.
